==============================================================
PROJECT: AI Creative Studio — Full SaaS Platform
Architecture: Website + Backend API + Electron Desktop App + Android APK
Inspired by: Wakanda Creatives (wakandacreatives.store) — reverse engineered
==============================================================

You are a senior full-stack developer. Build a complete, production-ready
AI creative studio platform with three interconnected components:
  1. A website (auth + billing + dashboard + admin)
  2. A backend API server (key validation + AI proxy + credit system)
  3. A desktop app (Electron — Windows EXE + auto-updater)
  4. An Android app (Capacitor WebView wrapper — APK sideload)

All three components communicate via a single API LICENSE KEY system.
The website issues keys, the app uses keys, the backend validates keys.

