==============================================================
IMPORTANT NOTES FOR DEVELOPER
==============================================================
- DO NOT implement account-sharing or credential-passing to users.
  All AI calls go through YOUR server using YOUR provider API keys only.
- Users only ever see their own API License Key (for app authentication).
  They never see or interact with your AI provider keys.
- The license key system is the security boundary:
  key → validates subscription → app gets permission to generate
  The AI provider is completely hidden from users.
- Code signing for Windows EXE is REQUIRED before launch.
  Windows Defender SmartScreen will block unsigned executables.
  Purchase a code signing certificate from Sectigo or DigiCert.
- Build electron-updater from day one, not as an afterthought.
- Set hard per-user daily generation limits to prevent API cost blowout.
  Suggested defaults: 20 images/day, 5 videos/day regardless of total credits.
